            <h2>Bands</h2>
            <h4>赤:H3 緑:H2 橙:混合<br>バンド名-演奏曲</h4>
            <div class="timetable-container" id="timetable-container">
            </div>
        </div>

    </main>

    <footer>
        ©︎2024 Keion Live PR
